505
00:27:50,002 --> 00:27:52,922
Hahn y Strassmann en Alemania.
Dividieron el núcleo de uranio.

506
00:27:54,257 --> 00:27:55,633
[Lawrence] ¿Cómo?

507
00:27:56,884 --> 00:27:58,719
Lo bombardearon con neutrones.

508
00:27:58,803 --> 00:28:01,472
