781
00:42:46,273 --> 00:42:48,483
O Tolman o
Rabi. Vas a.

782
00:42:51,653 --> 00:42:53,655
[charlando]

783
00:42:57,701 --> 00:42:59,327
[Oppenheimer] ¿Quiénes
